products.body_html:
Brand

Sandhurst

Product Claims

100% Fat Free

Ingredients

Quartered Artichoke Hearts (58%), Water, Salt, Citric Acid (E330).

Summary

Sandhurst Artichoke Hearts in Brine are plump, juicy, ready to eat out of the jar plus they're 100% Fat Free Use as a pizza topping or tossed over freshly cooked pasta or in a mixed salad.

Storage

Refrigerate after opening. eat within 14 days of opening.
